    cublasAtomicsMode

    cublasDiagType
    Indicates whether the main diagonal of the dense matrix is unity and consequently should not be touched or modified by the function.
    cublasFillMode
    Indicates which part (lower or upper) of the dense matrix was filled and consequently should be used by the function

    cublasPointerMode

Package jcuda.jcublas Description

Contains the classes of JCublas.

Package Specification

This package contains classes that are related to JCublas. The main class is the JCublas class, which provides all method bindings for CUBLAS, the NVIDIA CUDA BLAS library.

Please consult your CUBLAS library documentation for more information about how to use this API.
